4.NODE
*******************************
Node is a software
npm -command line installer called npm so that we can download any node modules
Add to Path-C:\Program Files (x86)\nodejs\node_modules\npm\bin

*******************************
5.INSTALL APPIUM
*******************************

Client-Appium Java Client(Eclipse IDE)
Server-Appium Server

npm install -g appium
-g means installing it globally

Once it is done
Type appium

To Uninstall-
npm uninstall -g appium


